Enum Measure.Aggregator

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Measure.Aggregator>
      • org.olap4j.metadata.Measure.Aggregator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<Measure.Aggregator>, XmlaConstant
    Enclosing interface:
    Measure

    public static enum Measure.Aggregator
extends Enum<Measure.Aggregator>
implements XmlaConstant
    Enumeration of the aggregate functions which can be used to derive a Measure.

    The values are as specified by XMLA. For example, XMLA specifies MDMEASURE_AGGR_SUM with ordinal 1, which corresponds to the value SUM, whose xmlaOrdinal is 1.
